!======================================================================
!
! *** isorropia code ii
! *** subroutine calcv5
! *** case v5
!
!     the main characteristics of this regime are:
!     1. sulfate poor (so4rat > 2.0), cr+na poor (crnarat < 2)
!     2. there is both a liquid & solid phase
