!
! *** isorropia code ii
! *** subroutine calcw4
! *** case w4
!
!     the main characteristics of this regime are:
!     1. sulfate poor (sulrat > 2.0) ; rcr+na >= 2.0 ; rcr > 2)
!     2. solid aerosol only
!     3. solids possible : caso4 , k2so4 , kno3 , kcl , mgso4 ,
!                          mg(no3)2 , nano3 , nacl , nh4no3 , nh4cl
!
